{"type": "article", "id": 22622, "title": "波浪线条椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122221GlbaYqke6pBj8xUQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是挪威设计师 Kristine Five Melvær 在斯德哥尔摩家具展上展出的椅子。圆形座位下的椅腿像是三个大波浪弧线，首尾相连，它实际将接口隐藏了起来。从不同角度看，3 个支撑结构则形成不同的几何造型，而连贯的结构既具有装饰性，也可以使得椅子显得简单轻盈。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122219AyXBYTE91sz4FRoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122219vapJegRQoIHAwc3V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122220l01b5zkNa2Uguxcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122220i7n3E9SQgj50ACyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122221nIsXPULSCdp1oWME.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92628205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}